data.message: Can't login my other Facebook please unlock

replies.message: Hi Coral. If you're having trouble logging into your Facebook account, here are a few things to try first: http://bit.ly/2w7eQJX. You can also learn how to regain access to your account here: http://bit.ly/2xoie6l. Additionally, if the problem continues, please report it to us: http://bit.ly/2xnodbv. Please keep in mind that is goes agains Facebook Community Standards to maintain more than one personal account. -Tenaya
